{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/\u629b\u74e6_720p.gif?t=1728383194\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Poetry of Blood: Eclipse</strong> is a hyper-speed 2D roguelite action game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the game, you will take on the role of a character codenamed\u00a0<i>Ishtar\u00a0</i>the female protagonist, \u201c<strong>Moon</strong>\u201d. Explore a post-apocalyptic world, defeat the beautiful girl bosses scattered across the land, and bring them back to your research base.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/soup.gif?t=1728383194\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use different weapons, equipment, and AI companions to fight enemies and explore the future world together![/p</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/Yue_Pixel.png?t=1728383194\" />  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/FukoCat.gif?t=1728383194\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/Fuko.gif?t=1728383194\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/IzumiNene.gif?t=1728383194\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/Noir.gif?t=1728383194\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/Robo_Pixel.png?t=1728383194\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/ShopMasterSteam.gif?t=1728383194\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/W_Pixel.png?t=1728383194\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Main Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master the mechanics of various weapons, including katanas, great katanas, spears, greatswords, chakrams, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Standard attacks, charged attacks, precision charged attacks, counters, rising attacks, and other general combat moves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Parry counter, blocking, dodging, perfect dodge, double jump, wall grab, ledge grab, dash glide, and other action elements.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/\u95ea\u907f\u53cd\u51fb+\u4e8c\u6bb5\u8df3.gif?t=1728383194\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In each challenge, choose different Tarot card entries to gain enhancement mechanics and corresponding attributes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reroll weapon enhancement entries in the shop, using limited resources and luck to pursue the maximum damage potential.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Consume &quot;Synthetic Blood&quot; to upgrade the out-of-game tech tree, continuously improving the character's basic abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore and collect items on the map, give gifts to increase NPC affinity, and learn about the unique stories and anecdotes of the beautiful girls.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/Sifu.gif?t=1728383194\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/Tsukuyomi_ATK2.gif?t=1728383194\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nearly all characters and enemies are hand-drawn in pixel art, with complex and fluid animations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A rich and diverse combat system featuring four basic classes and hundreds of Tarot card entries for endless combinations. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The EA version includes: 2 major stages and 5 sub-bosses (with hidden forms as well).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adorable pixel art girls: from base NPCs to powerful boss</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/ying_720p.gif?t=1728383194\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Thanks for your like and add to wishlist. This is the first game I've created and the first installment in Poetry of Blood series. I hope everyone will enjoy it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/thumbnail.png?t=1728383194\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"New moon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2372330/5c329d3342c3f62a27dd379ab4afdd81593644f5.jpg"},{"name":"Tsukuyomi!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2372330/588ec6c5dd6b7d2b71062274ffbcf43ceadec56e.jpg"},{"name":"Pure Blood I ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2372330/d92ffe47281f7c73ef3d71c8110dc1468c050bc6.jpg"},{"name":"Pure Blood II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2372330/9e5a9e2cc73fa8e8168fe770401eb5ca727976b1.jpg"},{"name":"Pure Blood III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2372330/207d0b1a6140277c412c93612d27ab2fcb2300da.jpg"},{"name":"Pure Blood IV","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2372330/891cd0d40f4a2d98f7482a7f96d6ae13a502d3f4.jpg"},{"name":"Pure Blood V","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.c